name: Melancholy
description:
Techcique: ballpiontpen on drawing paper.
Size: 21*29cm.

Deep inside the madness designed, you rot Hear this foretelling of crepuscule doom most feral The desolation of a human, an incarnate disgrace
Obliterate proceeds their fatal function, disease Devastation is the antidote Chanting for the anathema of grand dolor.
